Titolo: Condemned 2: Bloodshot

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Condemned 2: Bloodshot (titled Condemned 2 outside of North America) is a psychological survival horror video game, developed by Monolith Productions and published by Sega for the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 video game consoles. It is the sequel to the 2005 game Condemned: Criminal Origins. Due to its violent content, the game was indexed in Germany by the Federal Department for Media Harmful to Young Persons in April 2008 and subsequently banned in October.
Greg Grunberg does not reprise his role as Ethan Thomas in Condemned 2. Instead, Ethan is voiced by Andr√© Sogliuzzo.